      "content": "i mean it’s not a huge amount of fluid, just a little bit. i've got some antibiotic ointment in my medicine cabinet and i can just do warm compresses on it tonight? if i keep it clean and use the cream, it should clear up on its own right? i'd rather not pay for another doctor visit if i can just treat it at home.",
